♪Under a crescent moon,
I felt empty and emotional♪

535
00:48:44,673 --> 00:48:50,497
♪Afraid I would lost you forever
with mixed feelings♪

536
00:48:50,497 --> 00:48:58,241
♪Hope your eyes remain pure and warm
and our country splendid♪

